## Description

Implement a feature to save user-defined data snapshots, allowing users to specify the snapshot category and filename, and save the serialized data content to the corresponding snapshot file. The system uses the `fs` module's `writeFileSync` API for file writing, and constructs the final file path by joining the `/tmp/resources` directory with the user-provided category and filename using `path.join`. Users can control the category and filename parameters to facilitate categorized storage of temporary data snapshots by scenario.

